  • After device connected,press ERASE button
  • After erasing,unplug and open DTU8.
  • Rom should be a mess, don't care about that
  • press "load program file" at the lefttop corner of toolbar
  • Waiting for it to complete
  • Boom,a brand new cy 23d

Correct method to flash:
  • Connect calc VCC pad to 3v3 and vref
  • Pass 7v voltage to VPP pad
  • Open MWU16
  • Select the option read "init flash" in security screen/menu
  • After device connected,press ERASE button
  • Open DTU8
  • Rom should be a mess, don't care about that
  • Press "load program file" at the lefttop corner of toolbar
  • Wait a minute
  • (IMPORTANT!!!)After flashing, remove 7V VPP first then unplug uEASE
  • You should flash quickly or the MCU will be likely to get fried
  • Dumping ROM doesn't require 7v vpp

telecomadm1145
Correct method to flash:
  • Connect calc VCC pad to 3v3 and vref
  • Pass 7v voltage to VPP pad
  • Open MWU16
  • Select the option read "init flash" in security screen/menu
  • After device connected,press ERASE button
  • Open DTU8
  • Rom should be a mess, don't care about that
  • Press "load program file" at the lefttop corner of toolbar
  • Wait a minute
  • (IMPORTANT!!!)After flashing, remove 7V VPP first then unplug uEASE
  • You should flash quickly or the MCU will be likely to get fried
  • Dumping ROM doesn't require 7v vpp
 (edited)
